headline: Campbell’s Names Aaron Gwinner Chief Digital & Technology Officer
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., April 03, 2025--The Campbell’s Company (NASDAQ:CPB) (Campbell’s) today announced the appointment of Aaron Gwinner as Senior Vice President and Chief Digital & Technology Officer, effective April 14, 2025.
